<head /> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="296" /> On the <dateStruct value="--19" full="yes" authname="---19"><day reg="19" full="yes">19th instant</day></dateStruct>, at <placeName reg="St. Paul's Church">St. Paul's Church</placeName>, by <persName n="Minnegerode,Reverend,Charles,,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00189" reg="default:Minnegerode,Charles,,," authname="minnegerode,charles"><roleName n="Reverend" full="yes">the Rev.</roleName> <foreName full="yes">Charles</foreName> <surname full="yes">Minnegerode</surname>, <roleName n="Doctor of Divinity" full="yes">D. D.</roleName></persName>, <persName n="Pegram,Brigadier-General,John,,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00190" reg="default:Pegram,John,,," authname="pegram,john"><roleName n="Brigadier-General" full="yes">Brigadier- General</roleName> <foreName full="yes">John</foreName> <surname full="yes">Pegram</surname></persName>, <orgName n="Provisional Army" type="misc">Provisional Army</orgName> <placeName reg="United States" key="tgn,7012149" authname="tgn,7012149">Confederate States</placeName>, to <persName n="Cary,Miss,Heity,,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00191" reg="default:Cary,Heity,,," authname="cary,heity"><roleName n="Miss" full="yes">Miss.</roleName> <foreName full="yes">Heity</foreName> <surname full="yes">Cary</surname></persName>, of <placeName reg="Baltimore, Baltimore Independent City, Maryland" key="tgn,7013352" authname="tgn,7013352">Baltimore, Maryland</placeName>. </p> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="297" /> <placeName reg="Baltimore, Baltimore Independent City, Maryland" key="tgn,7013352" authname="tgn,7013352">Baltimore</placeName> papers please copy. </p> </div4> 
<div4 type="wed" n="2" org="uniform" sample="complete"> 
<head /> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="298" /> At the residence of the bride, on <date>Tuesday</date>, the <dateStruct value="--17" full="yes" authname="---17"><day reg="17" full="yes">17th instant</day></dateStruct>, by <persName n="Lumpkin,Reverend,,,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00192" reg="mostcommon:Lumpkin,nomatch:0" authname="lumpkin"><roleName n="Reverend" full="yes">the Rev. Mr.</roleName> <surname full="yes">Lumpkin</surname></persName>, <persName n="Livesay,,George,Washington,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00193" reg="default:Livesay,George,Washington,," authname="livesay,george,washington"><foreName full="yes">George</foreName> <foreName full="yes">Washington</foreName> <surname full="yes">Livesay</surname></persName>, <hi rend="smallcaps">Sr.,</hi> of <placeName reg="Hanover county, Virginia" key="tgn,1002451" authname="tgn,1002451">Hanover county</placeName>, and <persName n="Hudson,Mrs.,Emily,F.,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00194" reg="default:Hudson,Emily,F.,," authname="hudson,emily,f."><roleName n="Mrs." full="yes">Mrs.</roleName> <foreName full="yes">Emily</foreName> <foreName full="yes">F.</foreName> <surname full="yes">Hudson</surname></persName>, of <placeName reg="Henrico, Virginia" key="tgn,1002467" authname="tgn,1002467">Henrico county</placeName>. </p> </div4> 
<div4 type="wed" n="3" org="uniform" sample="complete"> 
<head /> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="299" /> In <placeName reg="New Kent, Virginia, United States" key="tgn,1002713" authname="tgn,1002713">New Kent county</placeName>, on the <dateStruct value="-01-12" full="yes" authname="--01-12"><day reg="12" full="yes">12th</day> of <month reg="01" full="yes">January</month></dateStruct>, by <persName n="Turner,Reverend,,,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00195" reg="mostcommon:Turner,nomatch:0" authname="turner"><roleName n="Reverend" full="yes">the Rev. Mr.</roleName> <surname full="yes">Turner</surname></persName>, <persName n="Wilkse,Mister,Thomas,C.,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00196" reg="default:Wilkse,Thomas,C.,," authname="wilkse,thomas,c."><roleName n="Mister" full="yes">Mr.</roleName> <foreName full="yes">Thomas</foreName> <foreName full="yes">C.</foreName> <surname full="yes">Wilkse</surname></persName>, <orgName type="company" n="Company F">company F</orgName>. <orgName type="regiment" key="3VACav">Third Virginia cavalry</orgName>, to <persName><foreName full="yes">Mollie</foreName></persName> P., the <num value="2" type="ordinal">second</num> daughter of <persName n="Epps,,John,E.,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00197" reg="default:Epps,John,E.,," authname="epps,john,e."><foreName full="yes">John</foreName> <foreName full="yes">E.</foreName> <surname full="yes">Epps</surname></persName>, of <placeName reg="Richmond, Richmond, Virginia" key="tgn,7013964" authname="tgn,7013964">Richmond, Virginia</placeName>. </p> </div4> </div3> 
<div3 type="death" n="2" org="uniform" sample="complete"> 
<head>Died.</head> 
<div4 type="obit" n="1" org="uniform" sample="complete"> 
<head /> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="300" /> On yesterday, of a short but extremely painful illness, <persName n="Henriques,Mrs.,Maria,,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00198" reg="default:Henriques,Maria,,," authname="henriques,maria"><roleName n="Mrs." full="yes">Mrs.</roleName> <foreName full="yes">Maria</foreName> <surname full="yes">Henriques</surname></persName>, in the <num value="80" type="ordinal">eightieth</num> year of her age. </p> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="301" /> Her funeral will take place on to-Morrow (<dateStruct full="yes"><day type="name" full="yes">Sunday</day></dateStruct>) at <placeName key="tgn,2060347" n="1.000 2" reg="saint james, phelps, missouri" authname="tgn,2060347">St. James</placeName>'s (<persName n="Peterkin,Reverend-Mister,,,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00199" reg="mostcommon:Peterkin,nomatch:0" authname="peterkin"><roleName n="Reverend-Mister" full="yes">Rev. Mr.</roleName> <surname full="yes">Peterkin</surname></persName>'s) Church at <time value="1pm">1 o'clock P. M.</time> Her friends are invited to attend. </p> </div4> 
<div4 type="obit" n="2" org="uniform" sample="complete"> 
<head /> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="302" /> In this city, on the <dateStruct value="-01-12" full="yes" authname="--01-12"><day reg="12" full="yes">12th</day> of <month reg="01" full="yes">January</month></dateStruct>, by <persName n="Pettigrew,Reverend,,,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00200" reg="mostcommon:Pettigrew,nomatch:0" authname="pettigrew"><roleName n="Reverend" full="yes">the Rev. Mr.</roleName> <surname full="yes">Pettigrew</surname></persName>, <persName n="Wilson,Mister,James,W.,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00201" reg="default:Wilson,James,W.,," authname="wilson,james,w."><roleName n="Mister" full="yes">Mr.</roleName> <foreName full="yes">James</foreName> <foreName full="yes">W.</foreName> <surname full="yes">Wilson</surname></persName>, of <placeName reg="Petersburg, Petersburg, Virginia" key="tgn,7014404" authname="tgn,7014404">Petersburg</placeName>, to <persName n="Shunburger,Miss,Martha,,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00202" reg="default:Shunburger,Martha,,," authname="shunburger,martha"><roleName n="Miss" full="yes">Miss.</roleName> <foreName full="yes">Martha</foreName> <surname full="yes">Shunburger</surname></persName>, of this city. </p> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="303" /> <placeName reg="Norfolk, Norfolk, Virginia" key="tgn,7014231" authname="tgn,7014231">Norfolk</placeName> and <placeName reg="Petersburg, Petersburg, Virginia" key="tgn,7014404" authname="tgn,7014404">Petersburg</placeName> papers please copy. </p> </div4> 
<div4 type="obit" n="3" org="uniform" sample="complete"> 
<head /> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="304" /> On the <dateStruct value="--19" full="yes" authname="---19"><day reg="19" full="yes">19th instant</day></dateStruct>, <persName n="Fergusson,Doctor,William,C.,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00203" reg="default:Fergusson,William,C.,," authname="fergusson,william,c."><roleName n="Doctor" full="yes">Dr.</roleName> <foreName full="yes">William</foreName> <foreName full="yes">C.</foreName> <surname full="yes">Fergusson</surname></persName>, late of <placeName reg="Charles City, Virginia, United States" key="tgn,1002257" authname="tgn,1002257">Charles City county</placeName>, in the <num value="28" type="ordinal">twenty- eighth</num> year of his age. </p> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="305" /> His funeral will take place from <orgName n="St.James Church" type="church">St. James' Church</orgName> to-day at <time value="12oclock">12 o'clock</time>. His friends and acquaintances are invited to attend. </p> </div4> 
<div4 type="obit" n="4" org="uniform" sample="complete"> 
<head /> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="306" /> On <dateStruct value="-01-20" full="yes" authname="--01-20"><day type="name" full="yes">Friday</day>, <month reg="01" full="yes">January</month> <day reg="20" full="yes">20th</day></dateStruct>, <persName><foreName full="yes">Sallie</foreName></persName> A, wife of <persName n="Parker,,George,C.,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00204" reg="default:Parker,George,C.,," authname="parker,george,c."><foreName full="yes">George</foreName> <foreName full="yes">C.</foreName> <surname full="yes">Parker</surname></persName>, in the <num value="32" type="ordinal">thirty-second</num> year of her age. </p> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="307" /> The friends and acquaintances of the family are requested to attend her funeral from <address><street n="Leigh Street">Leigh Street</street></address> <orgName n="Baptist Church" type="church">Baptist Church</orgName> on to-Morrow (<dateStruct full="yes"><day type="name" full="yes">Sunday</day></dateStruct>) Afternoon at <time value="2:30oclock">half-past 2 o'clock</time>. </p> </div4> 
<div4 type="obit" n="5" org="uniform" sample="complete"> 
<head /> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="308" /> On the <dateStruct value="1864-10-29" full="yes" authname="1864-10-29"><day reg="29" full="yes">29th</day> of <month reg="10" full="yes">October</month>, <year full="yes">1864</year>,</dateStruct> at hospital at <placeName key="possibilities=31" n="1.000 10" reg="," authname="possibilities=31">Point of Rocks</placeName>, <persName n="Baker,,Frederick,W.,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00205" reg="default:Baker,Frederick,W.,," authname="baker,frederick,w."><foreName full="yes">Frederick</foreName> <foreName full="yes">W.</foreName> <surname full="yes">Baker</surname></persName>, aged <measure n="43years" type="date">forty- three years</measure> and <measure n="6months" type="date">six months</measure>. </p> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="309" /> He was wounded on the <dateStruct value="1864-09-30" full="yes" authname="1864-09-30"><day reg="30" full="yes">30th</day> of <month reg="09" full="yes">September</month>, <year full="yes">1864</year>,</dateStruct> below <placeName key="tgn,7013964" n="1.000 9" reg="richmond, richmond, virginia" authname="tgn,7013964">Richmond</placeName>.

<milestone unit="sentence" n="310" />He leaves a wife and <num value="5">five</num> children to mourn their irreparable loss. </p> </div4> </div3> </div2> 
