<div2 type="negroes" org="uniform" sample="complete"> 
<head>Negroes for Hire and Sale.</head> 
<div3 type="article" n="1" org="uniform" sample="complete"> 
<head /> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="347" />For Sale, Privately, a Woman of good character, with <num value="1">one</num> Child a year old. She is a <num value="1" type="ordinal">first</num>-rate seamstress, house servant.

<milestone unit="sentence" n="348" />Main cook, and good washer and ironer; sold for no fault whatever, and can be highly recommended as a most faithful, trusty servant.

<milestone unit="sentence" n="349" />The owner wishes to secure a good home for her in the city.

<milestone unit="sentence" n="350" />Address <measure value="box 854" type="box">box 854</measure>. </p> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="351" /> <term type="printrun">ja 21--1t</term> </p> </div3> 
<div3 type="article" n="2" org="uniform" sample="complete"> 
<head /> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="352" />For Hire, a <num value="1">No. 1</num> Negro Man, as <persName n="Porter,,,,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00237" reg="nearbymention:Porter,David,D.,," authname="porter,david,d."><surname full="yes">Porter</surname></persName> or <persName n="Packer,,,,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00238" reg="mostcommon:Packer,nomatch:0" authname="packer"><surname full="yes">Packer</surname></persName> in a drug store; has had several years' experience.

<milestone unit="sentence" n="353" />Also, <num value="1">one</num> who has had much experience in commission and wholesale houses.

<milestone unit="sentence" n="354" />Both are honest and capable in every respect.

<milestone unit="sentence" n="355" />Address Refugee, <orgName n="Dispatch office" type="office">Dispatch office</orgName>. </p> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="356" /> <term type="printrun">ja 21--3t</term> </p> </div3> 
<div3 type="article" n="3" org="uniform" sample="complete"> 
<head /> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="357" />For Hire, <num value="1">one</num> or <num value="2">two</num> little Girls, very active and likely, and accustomed to every description of house work.

<milestone unit="sentence" n="358" />To obtain good homes, they will be hired at merely nominal prices.

<milestone unit="sentence" n="359" />Apply at the corner of <address><street n="22 Street">Twenty-second</street></address> and <address><street n="Broad Street">Broad streets</street></address>. </p> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="360" /> <term type="printrun">ja 19--3t</term> </p> </div3> </div2> 
