<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="380" />Notice to Holders and Owners of <num value="0.06">Six Per Cent.</num> Non-Taxable Certificates of Indebtedness, Issued under the <orgName type="regiment" key="14Section">Fourteenth Section</orgName> of Act of <dateStruct value="1864-02-17" full="yes" authname="1864-02-17"><month reg="02" full="yes">February</month> <day reg="17" full="yes">17</day>, <year reg="1864" full="yes">1864</year></dateStruct>.--Notice is hereby given to holders and owners of <num value="0.06">Six Per Cent.</num> Non-Taxable Certificates of Indebtedness, issued under the <orgName type="regiment" key="14Section">fourteenth section</orgName> of the act of <dateStruct value="1864-02-17" full="yes" authname="1864-02-17"><month reg="02" full="yes">February</month> <day reg="17" full="yes">17</day>, <year reg="1864" full="yes">1864</year></dateStruct>, that the interest due on the same to <dateStruct value="1865-01-21" full="yes" authname="1865-01-21"><day reg="21" full="yes">21st</day> <month reg="01" full="yes">January</month>, <year full="yes">1865</year>,</dateStruct> will be paid upon presentation of the bonds of any time after <dateStruct value="-01-1" full="yes" authname="--01-01"><day reg="1" full="yes">1st</day> <month reg="01" full="yes">January</month></dateStruct> to the <rs>Treasurer</rs>, <rs type="role" reg="Assistant-Treasurer">Assistant Treasurer</rs> or Pay Depositaries named below. </p> <closer> <signed><persName n="Trenholm,,G.,A.,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00248" reg="default:Trenholm,G.,A.,," authname="trenholm,g.,a."><foreName full="yes">G.</foreName> <foreName full="yes">A.</foreName>  <surname full="yes">Trenholm</surname></persName>,</signed> <lb /> <signed><rs type="role" reg="Secretary of the Treasury">Secretary of Treasury</rs>.</signed> <lb /> <signed>Treasurer at <placeName reg="Richmond, Richmond, Virginia" key="tgn,7013964" authname="tgn,7013964">Richmond, Virginia</placeName>.</signed> <lb /> <signed><rs type="role" reg="Assistan